{"tid":746770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門水管老化一年爆四次　水務署被批更換進度太慢","createTime":"2018-07-18T00:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T00:13:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"36370556746009fdf91556cfa055fb042388d873","tid":746770,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T00:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1639244/org/ac588f1da5c6357155ac1ab6af168697.jpg/xEYts3gK2czJeS0gIgZx2mzjHPeySSBVpo1wf6aNcH8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1639244%2Forg%2Fac588f1da5c6357155ac1ab6af168697.jpg%2FxEYts3gK2czJeS0gIgZx2mzjHPeySSBVpo1wf6aNcH8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f940711f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門碼頭區水管老化，過去一年至少4次爆水管，嚴重影響民生和交通，居民不勝其煩，屯門區議會明日將與水務處開會跟進。有屯門區議員批評，水務署更換水管的工程進度非常緩慢，「更換一段水管，另一段水管又爆」，要求政府增撥資源加快更換水管進度。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》記者翻查資料，發現屯門碼頭區，特別湖翠路及龍門路一帶地下水管過去一年已發生至少4次爆水管，幾乎每隔數月就有一次，令事發路段需要全線封閉，導致大塞車，多條巴士因封路改道。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1639263/org/03105fa9b99791a17b56ae18401714f7.JPG/JwRcb6LGviQr90na_Zojdy0Mkl4JufQcRUK0S0VCtEs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1639263%2Forg%2F03105fa9b99791a17b56ae18401714f7.JPG%2FJwRcb6LGviQr90na_Zojdy0Mkl4JufQcRUK0S0VCtEs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b6a67a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過去一年屯門碼頭區爆水管事件簿（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n屯門區議員楊智恒稱，爆水管問題已困擾屯門居民多年，不但嚴重影響該區的鹹水供應，對區內行動不便的長者造成不便，亦擾亂該區路面交通安全，居民無法按時工作上學。<br />\n<br />\n楊智恒指出，該區近年多次爆水管，反映水管老化問題極為嚴重，過去屯門區議會已多次向水務署及有關部門反映，應提昇工程級別，優先增撥資源更換該區水管，惟水務署更換水管的工程進度實在緩慢，「每次逐小段更換，更換一段水管，另一段水管又爆」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1639296/org/7acc2c257f3171ae8fe96727dc97c4b8.jpg/O-_HD9FBGW9Duo1DLMMYS56sNSizGpefQlU_I0JVPyM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1639296%2Forg%2F7acc2c257f3171ae8fe96727dc97c4b8.jpg%2FO-_HD9FBGW9Duo1DLMMYS56sNSizGpefQlU_I0JVPyM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=96abc6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門碼頭近美樂花園出口對開，去年初曾發生鹹水管爆裂。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>完工期一拖再拖</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水務署回覆屯門區議會指，近年屯門碼頭區經常爆水管，主因是一段沿湖翠路至龍門路、直徑900毫米的鹹水管管喉老化造成，該段水管已納入水管改善計畫，有關工程已展開，預計明年中完工。<br />\n<br />\n記者翻查2011年財務委員會工務小姐文件，水務署原於2000年起展開「更換及修復水管計劃」，分階段全面更換及修復長約全港3000公里的老化水管，以改善供水網絡的狀況，預計2015年完成。<br />\n<br />\n惟計畫工程完工期一拖再拖，據楊智恆提供的水務署資料顯示，由屯門鹹水抽水站沿湖翠路至龍門路約600米鹹水水管，至今只為其中湖翠路約200米水管已經完成更換及接駁入現存供水系統，餘下約400米水管改善工程仍需分兩期進行，要明年中才竣工。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1639788/org/8c997f1eca4bddfc8e1063cc14265b3d.JPG/f1oRxPm3dnu3hJmKHIcqh8AZ4mp3FNhmL4yWei-Mlno?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1639788%2Forg%2F8c997f1eca4bddfc8e1063cc14265b3d.JPG%2Ff1oRxPm3dnu3hJmKHIcqh8AZ4mp3FNhmL4yWei-Mlno%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b7ab5bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門龍門路及湖翠路鹹水水管修復工程進度。（受訪者提供）<br />\n<br />\n撰文：李智智<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/210023/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E8%80%81%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%88%86%E5%9B%9B%E6%AC%A1-%E6%B0%B4%E5%8B%99%E7%BD%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E6%9B%B4%E6%8F%9B%E9%80%B2%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%AA%E6%85%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F210023%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%258C%2596%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%25AC%25A1-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%258B%2599%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%258F%259B%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%2585%25A2&d=tOLpo1X6ylTatJXlymuDVgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8cce7f38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/210023/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E8%80%81%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%88%86%E5%9B%9B%E6%AC%A1-%E6%B0%B4%E5%8B%99%E7%BD%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E6%9B%B4%E6%8F%9B%E9%80%B2%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%AA%E6%85%A2</a>"},{"pid":"31edc8572bd2d285040e8b0fa28cfd8b12c51ab2","tid":746770,"uid":17907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T00:02:27.000Z","msg":"成日無廁所水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74038fa5e11e4f00fc9eee3e01a0756f4d5adbf","tid":746770,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T00:13:18.000Z","msg":"做咁快做咩，有句叫長做長有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}